                        "text": "\ud83d\udccc Save this for when you visit Paris \ud83c\uddeb\ud83c\uddf7\u2728\n\n\ud83d\udccdCaf\u00e9 - Restaurant Le Jardin du Petit Palais\n\nLocated in the heart of my favorite museum, Petit Palais, this cafe is a hidden gem that you can\u2019t miss! When you visit, I highly recommend sitting on the terrace and soaking up the beauty of the museum, fountain, and garden while having a delicious lunch. Petit Palais is free to enter, so you can visit this cafe for free as well! \ud83c\udf74\n\nHave you heard of this cafe before? \ud83e\udd0d\n\nFollow\u00a0@helloangelia\u00a0for more travel tips around the world \u2728\n\n#parisfrance\u00a0#visitparis\u00a0#exploreparis\u00a0#exploreeurope\u00a0#visiteurope\u00a0#parisvibes #europetrip Paris France, Paris restaurant, travel reels, europe travel, European summer"
